uk.gov.gchq.palisade.redirect.service

Class HeartbeatRedirector<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.redirect.service.HeartbeatRedirector<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Redirector<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleRandomRedirector

    public abstract class HeartbeatRedirector<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Redirector<T>
    A base redirector class that can be used to implement other redirectors. Sub-classes should call isRedirectionValid(String, String, Method, Object...) before returning a definite result.
